videos.headline: UTSA's Franklin scores go-ahead TD
videos.description: UTSA QB Lowell Narcisse connects with Zakhari Franklin in the end zone for an eight-yard touchdown to give the Roadrunners a 31-27 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (UTSA's Franklin scores go-ahead TD) 2019/10/19
